<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .header img {
      width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #007bff;
    }
    .content {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .details-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .details-table th, .details-table td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .details-table th {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #888;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://b3700355.smushcdn.com/3700355/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/unnamed.png?lossy=2&strip=1&webp=1" alt="PK Photography Logo">
      <h1>New Booking Notification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>A new booking has been made by the client. Here are the details:</p>
      <table class="details-table">
        <tr>
          <th>Name</th>
          <td><%= name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Email</th>
          <td><%= email %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Phone</th>
          <td><%= phone %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Address</th>
          <td><%= address %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Service</th>
          <td><%= service %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Message</th>
          <td><%= message %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Date</th>
          <td><%= date %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Time</th>
          <td><%= time %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p>Please follow up with the client for confirmation.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p><strong>PK Photography Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2024 PK Photography, Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:support@pkphotography.io">Contact Us</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
